---
title: HelloHero: Italian Pork Fusilli with Baby Leaves & Cheddar Cheese
description: Pasta with a cheesy tomato sauce, veggies and the combo of  pork, all packed into one amazing piled-high pasta. If that’s what you were hoping for then this dish won’t disappoint you!

*We’ve replaced the orecchiette in this recipe with fusilli due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*

